NO OF CALCULATION FIELDS
--------------------------------------
A key highlight of this analysis is the use of a calculated field to define Age Groups. Instead of using raw age values, customers are categorized into meaningful segments using the following logic:

- Age ≤ 20 → Child

- Age 21–30 → Gen Z

- Age 31–40 → Millennial

- Age > 40 → Adults

This calculated field enables better segmentation and simplifies analysis by grouping customers into interpretable categories.

